#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"A delicate blend of soft pink roses and baby's breath, perfect for "
"expressing love and gratitude."
msgstr ""
"Eine zarte Mischung aus zartrosa Rosen und Schleierkraut, perfekt, um Liebe "
"und Dankbarkeit auszudrücken."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline Turner, Bouquet Designer"
msgstr "Aline Turner, Blumenstraußdesignerin"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline is the mastermind behind our bespoke floral arrangements."
msgstr "Aline ist der Kopf hinter unseren maßgeschneiderten Blumengestecke."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_kickoff
msgid "Bloom with Joy:"
msgstr "Erblühen Sie voller Freude:"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Blushing Harmony"
msgstr "Blühende Harmonie"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text_overlap
msgid ""
"Brighten any corner of the globe with our express 24-hour worldwide flower "
"delivery service."
msgstr ""
"Verschönern Sie jeden Winkel der Erde mit unserem Express-"
"Blumenlieferdienst, der weltweit innerhalb von 24 Stunden liefert."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Bringing the Beauty of Nature to Your Space"
msgstr "Die Schönheit der Natur in Ihrem Wohnraum"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Celebrate with Our Best-Selling Bouquets, perfect for every occasion."
msgstr ""
"Feiern Sie mit unseren Bestseller-Blumensträußen, die sich perfekt für jeden "
"Anlass eignen."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Discover Our Most Loved Arrangements"
msgstr "Entdecken Sie unsere besten Blumengestecke"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_orchid.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Anzeigename"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Elegant Simplicity"
msgstr "Elegante Einfachheit"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid ""
"Enhance your surroundings with our exquisite floral arrangements and garden "
"designs. We offer a variety of options that bring the serenity and beauty of "
"nature into your home or workspace."
msgstr ""
"Verschönern Sie Ihre Umgebung mit unseren exquisiten Blumengestecken und "
"Pflanzen. Wir bieten eine Vielzahl von Optionen, die die Ruhe und Schönheit "
"der Natur in Ihr Zuhause oder Ihren Arbeitsbereich bringen."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Explore Our Gardens"
msgstr "Entdecken Sie unsere Gärten"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_title
msgid ""
"Explore our handcrafted floral arrangements, each meticulously designed to "
"convey beauty, elegance, and a touch of nature's artistry."
msgstr ""
"Entdecken Sie unsere handgefertigten Blumengestecke, die alle sorgfältig "
"gestaltet wurden, um Schönheit, Eleganz und einen Hauch von Naturkunst zu "
"vermitteln."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_kickoff
msgid "Fresh Flowers Delivered to Your Doorstep!"
msgstr "Frische Blumen direkt an die Haustür!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text_overlap
msgid "Global 24-Hour Flower Delivery"
msgstr "Weltweiter 24-Stunden-Blumenversand"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_orchid.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Iris Joe, Customer Relations"
msgstr "Iris Joe, Kundenbeziehungen"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Iris ensures that each customer has a delightful experience."
msgstr "Iris sorgt dafür, dass jeder Kunde ein angenehmes Erlebnis hat."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"Light pink blossoms with golden leaves, bringing a touch of springtime charm "
"to any space."
msgstr ""
"Hellrosa Blüten mit goldenen Blättern, die jedem Raum einen Hauch von "
"Frühlingszauber verleihen."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Meet the Team"
msgstr "Das Team kennenlernen"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Mich Stark, Operations Manager"
msgstr "Mich Stark, Betriebsleiter"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Mich makes sure everything runs smoothly."
msgstr "Mich sorgt dafür, dass alles reibungslos läuft."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"Minimalist white florals in a sleek vase, embodying sophistication and grace."
msgstr ""
"Minimalistische weiße Blumen in einer schlichten Vase, die Raffinesse und "
"Anmut verkörpern."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_title
msgid "Our Creations"
msgstr "Unsere Kreationen"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Petal Poetry"
msgstr "Blütenpoesie"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Sunset Serenade"
msgstr "Sunset Serenade"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_orchid.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Designwerkzeuge"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Tony Fred, Floral Director"
msgstr "Tony Fred, Blumenhändler"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Tony leads the creative vision for the shop."
msgstr "Tony hat die kreative Vision für den Shop."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"Vibrant hues of orange and red capture the warmth and beauty of a summer "
"evening."
msgstr ""
"Leuchtende Orange- und Rottöne fangen die Wärme und Schönheit eines "
"Sommerabends ein."
